OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA sunny
OL,6,Fevening for most but some low cloud
OL,7,Fwill affect the east coast. Dry with
OL,8,Fclear spells overnight but low cloud
OL,9,Fwill feed inland over the Lothians and
OL,10,FBorders.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FEarly low cloud in east will
OL,13,Fmostly burn off but some will continue
OL,14,Fto afflict the coasts. Otherwise,
OL,15,Fanother dry day with plenty of
OL,16,Fsunshine. Becoming very warm in west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
